headline: eBay (EBAY): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q1 Earnings?
summary: Even during a down period for the markets, eBay has gone against the grain, climbing to $72.71. Its shares have yielded a 15.1% return over the last six months, beating the S&P 500 by 17.4%. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
